name: Yancheng
description: Medium: Copper Etching  What is the world like in your eyes? Beautiful and harmonious? Sad and heavy? In this moment, I see a slice of life, where we cannot change the status quo. In modern cities, industrial smog has repeatedly poured into the clouds. Is it a gray cloud or a trace of modernization?
